statements.sql: select "id", (select count(*) from "likes" where "blogs"."id" = "likes"."likeable_id" and "likes"."likeable_type" = 'App\Models\Blog') as "likes_count", (select count(*) from "blog_comments" where "blogs"."id" = "blog_comments"."blog_id") as "comments_count" from "blogs" where "blogs"."id" in (1)

select "blog_comments".*, (select count(*) from "likes" where "blog_comments"."id" = "likes"."likeable_id" and "likes"."likeable_type" = 'App\Models\BlogComment') as "likes_count", (select count(*) from "blog_comments" as "laravel_reserved_0" where "blog_comments"."id" = "laravel_reserved_0"."parent_id") as "replies_count" from "blog_comments" where "blog_comments"."blog_id" in (1) order by "created_at" desc
select * from "likes" where "likes"."likeable_id" in (5, 16, 17, 19, 31) and "likes"."likeable_type" = 'App\Models\BlogComment' and "user_id" = 4

select "blog_comments".*, (select count(*) from "likes" where "blog_comments"."id" = "likes"."likeable_id" and "likes"."likeable_type" = 'App\Models\BlogComment') as "likes_count" from "blog_comments" where "blog_comments"."parent_id" in (5, 16, 17, 19, 31) order by "created_at" desc
select * from "likes" where "likes"."likeable_id" in (16, 17) and "likes"."likeable_type" = 'App\Models\BlogComment' and "user_id" = 4

select "roles".*, "model_has_roles"."model_id" as "pivot_model_id", "model_has_roles"."role_id" as "pivot_role_id", "model_has_roles"."model_type" as "pivot_model_type" from "roles" inner join "model_has_roles" on "roles"."id" = "model_has_roles"."role_id" where "model_has_roles"."model_id" in (3) and "model_has_roles"."model_type" = 'App\Models\User'
